Class Transition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgrapht.graph.DefaultEdge

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class Transition
extends org.jgrapht.graph.DefaultEdge
    Represents a transition of an automaton.
    A transition is identified by an id and is labeled by propositions. See Transition.
    Author:
    claudio menghi
